cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.SI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on privacy-preserving techniques such as differential privacy and homomorphic encryption.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper applies deep learning to the task of predicting readmission from electronic health records.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses AI techniques to address the privacy-utility trade-off in deploying neural networks with privacy mechanisms.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is a possible category as the paper deals with privacy concerns in the context of electronic health records.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is another possible category as the paper deals with privacy concerns in the context of sensitive personal data.
